            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6431693,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 映泰(2399)股價拉至漲停，漲停價43.65元，成交41,769張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>映泰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2399:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2399\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2399-TW</a>)24日13:09上漲3.95元，股價漲停報43.65元，委買12張、委賣3,091張，成交41,769張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電腦主機板。工業電腦。電腦VGA 卡。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>映泰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2399:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2399\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2399-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲13.43%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.57%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+62 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-163 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-154 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+379 張</li> <li>融資增減：+599 張</li> <li>融券增減：+215 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
